N/A.keyword: This is the list header field for the standard access list, which is a 3-dimensional array consisting of the ACLID, ACLACS, and ACLACNT fields. For generic profiles, the ACLACNT field does not apply, and the array will be 2-dimensional.

This is the list header field for the conditional access list, which is a 5-dimensional array consisting of the ACL2ID, ACL2ACS, ACL2ACNT, ACL2COND, and ACL2ENT fields. For generic profiles, the ACL2ACNT field does not apply, and the array will be 4-dimensional.
